nts are perpetual, though. There\u2019s a 7-day refund policy in place, allowing you the opportunity to give these guys a shot. If you give these guys a try as a result of this post, please share your experiences with us in the comments! <span id=\"more-6885\"></span> PayPal is currently the only available payment method (and credit cards through PayPal), though more should be added soon. IPv6 is not currently available. SMTP ports are blocked by default. Removing this block is an option, though you\u2019d waive your right for a refund. For more details, please read their <a href=\"https://linuxservers.host/policies/terms-and-conditions/\">Terms of Service</a> and <a href=\"https://linuxservers.host/policies/acceptable-use-policy/\">Acceptable Use Policy</a>.</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">CloudSouth \u2013 West Palm Beach, Florida, USA<br>\n</span>Test IPv4: 38.130.222.134<br>\nTest file: <a href=\"http://ns1.linuxservers.host/100MB.test\">http://ns1.linuxservers.host/100MB.test<br>\n</a>Looking glass: <a href=\"http://ns1.linuxservers.host\">http://ns1.linuxservers.host</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flinuxservers-host-openvz-vps-in-west-palm-beach-starting-at-3month-for-512mb%2F&amp;t=LinuxServers.host%20-%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20West%20Palm%20Beach%20starting%20at%20%243%2Fmonth%20for%20512MB\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-ne